rComments: The content of the course is useful. Homework is relatively easy as long as you pay attention to details. Prof Chadda answers email fast and is willing to help. Overall good course and great Prof.

Class was an easy A but I felt like he completely screwed over everyone on participation just to keep the class average lower than what it would have been.. even if you participated and showed to up to every class he would give 5 or 6 out of 10 wtf

One of the more easy-going classes of my third year. Pay attention and contribute in class and RSM455 is relatively easy. The assignments are an application of what was taught in class, with minimal background needed from the readings - they are not difficult, just make sure you start on time. I recommend this course to those who attend lectures
